title: 2021 North 2 Region wrestling: Wrestleback semifinal results (Reg. 3 & 4)
body: 2021 NJSIAA North 2 Region Wrestling ChampionshipsThe best high school boys wrestlers in New Jersey open pursuit of state titles on Saturday with the opening round of the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament.The North Jersey, Section 2 Region tournament is set for Union High School.Complete results are on the way from , so stay tuned.The wrestleback semifinals:3-, North Hunterdon d. 8-, Seton Hall Prep, 3-0.1-, Livingston d. 6-, Elizabeth, 12-5.4-, Livingston d. 3-, St. Peter's Prep, 6-4 (UTB).5-, Delbarton d. 7-, Morristown, 5-3.2-, Rahway d. 8-, Caldwell, 6-1.4-, Phillipsburg d. 6-, St. Peter's Prep, 8-3.3-, Mendham d. 9-, South Plainfield, 7-2.1-, St. Peter's Prep d. 6-, Rahway, 5-2.2-, St. Peter's Prep md. 4-, Hanover Park, 9-1.5-, Mendham d. 6-, North Hunterdon, 2-0.5-, Delbarton d. 7-, Phillipsburg, 7-3.6-, Cranford d. 4-, Morristown, 5-3.4-, St. Thomas Aquinas d. 6-, St. Peter's Prep, 9-7.7-, Brearley p. 5-, Phillipsburg, 3:00.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
